data.description: Sitting on .77 acre tidal Creek in Salem Point, this charming 3bedroom, 3.5bathroom recently upgraded home offers a tranquil lifestyle.Enjoy the Marsh/Sunset views with a giant angel oak.Upon entering,you are greeted with an open floorplan, a well-appointed kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances, and a spacious dining area. The large primary bedroom showcases an ensuite with dual vanity, soaking tub, and walk-in shower & bonus Room! Oversized yard backing the Beautiful marsh/creek offering an abundance of space to host your next gathering. This home offers a detached 2-car garage, carport, and workshop. Do not miss this opportunity!
